 <H1>Our Approach</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Uniform semantic base
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>model both architectural structure and abstract behavior
<LI>permits analysis of interactions between the two
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Syntactic separation between reconfiguration and �steady-state� behavior
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>localizes reconfiguration changes
<LI>separates concerns
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Limit specifications to common case of finite sets of configurations
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>supports static analysis</UL></UL></P>
